" AUTOCOMPLETE:
" The good stuff is documented in |ins-completion|
"   - ^x^n for JUST this file ( ^a^b means hold ctrl  )
"   - ^x^f for filenames (works with our path trick!)
"   - ^x^] for tags only
"   - ^n for anything specified by the 'complete' option

